snippet.textDisplay:
Heres why the coronavirus is nothing to worry about healthwise. I LOVE DIY videos but this needs to be said.

80,000 people die from flu in America yearly. But the coronavirus has only killed around 5,000 people in the ENTIRE country of China. South Korea also has extremely low mortality rates.
We get these numbers from the World Health Organisation (WHO). The WHO collects data from an enormous network of cooperative doctors and scientists that have boots on the ground in every country in the world.
The WHO has put out a statement that the coronavirus is far, far less lethal than the flu and also is reprimanding the media for grossly misreportimg and inflating the statistics.
If a country is reporting much higher fatality rates than China you should be extemely suspicious because it defies logic.
The news is reporting everyone that is infected with the covid-19 that dies in the hospital as a covid-19 related death even if they die from a heart attack or car accident. Or just that the show the symptoms before death without confirming it through tests. The media will use every crack and crevice to make the coronavirus seem way more dangerous than it is.

I apologise for ruffling any feathers because this video is nice and it seems the people who have watched it are beautiful people who are just doing beautiful things. Yall are beautiful.

Please do the math for yourself and dont believe the television/facebook until you have checked and confirmed the information for yourself.
Here is one of many doctors in the WHO network that has been fighting against the bizarre hysteria. https://youtu.be/p_AyuhbnPOI
